OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry today with very
OL,6,Fwarm sunny spells. A little cloud will
OL,7,Fbubble up in the afternoon across the
OL,8,Fregion perhaps with a few showers
OL,9,Flater in the afternoon. Feeling very
OL,10,Fwarm in the sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and warm evening with
OL,13,Flate sunshine. Skies will cloud over
OL,14,Fthrough the night with some outbreaks
OL,15,Fof rain in the early hours.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy at first in the morning
OL,18,Fwith a few showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,19,FTurning drier through the day with
OL,20,Fincreasing amounts of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
